name: sap.watt.common.service.ui.WizardFinishStep
description: The interface for the last step of a wizard. Any wizard final step is a WizardPart interface whose getContent method initiates the step UI (extending the sap.watt.uitools.plugin.template.ui.wizard.WizardStepContent parameter) with the this.context property. The getContent method then returns the result of the getWizardStep method of the wizard service with the WizardStep interface content object.
